item.description:
Memorial weekend golf at this semi-private country club in Georgetown, MA.  We have played here last year.

11:30 brunch beforehand is optional and costs $19.99 per person + tax, gratuity and any alcohol.

The menu is extensive:

Assorted pastries, muffins and breads Fresh fruit, yogurt and granola, assortment of cold salads, Sausage and bacon, Aged Vermont cheddar scrambled eggs, Home fries, French toast, Cheese blintz with fruit sauce, Belgian waffle station, Omelet station with all the fixings, Eggs benedict, Chef’s choice pasta, Ritz crusted haddock, Mixed vegetables Mac & cheese, Carving station with turkey and ham, and assorted desserts.  Plus a Build Your Own Bloody Mary Table!

Here is the link:

http://events.blackswancountryclub.com
